Build a modern responsive wholesale ecommerce web application using Next.js 15, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, MongoDB and Server Actions.

Application Name:
WholesaleHub

Target Users:
1. Admin
2. Vendor (Wholesale shop / Dealer / Distributor)
3. Buyer (Retail shop / Normal customer)

====================================================
CORE REQUIREMENTS
====================================================

The application should be:
- Very simple UI
- Mobile responsive
- Fast loading
- Easy for non-technical wholesalers
- Dashboard based
- Clean modern design
- Authentication based role system

Use:
- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- NextAuth/Auth.js authentication
- Tailwind CSS
- Shadcn UI
- React Hook Form + Zod validation
- TanStack Table
- Recharts for analytics
- Server Actions where possible

