====================================================
ORDER FLOW
====================================================

Buyer places order
→ Order automatically added to Vendor Google Sheet

====================================================
GOOGLE SHEET INTEGRATION
====================================================

IMPORTANT:
Each vendor should have separate Google Sheet integration.

Vendor Settings:
- Google Sheet ID
- Google Service Account Credentials
- Enable/Disable sync

When order placed:
Automatically append order data into vendor’s Google Sheet.

Sheet Columns:
- Order ID
- Date
- Buyer Name
- Buyer Phone
- Product Names
- Quantity
- Total Amount
- Payment Status
- Order Status

Use:
- Google Sheets API
- googleapis npm package

Create reusable utility:
- appendOrderToGoogleSheet()

